---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/base-layout.astro";
import SiteHeader from "@components/site-header.astro";

const title = "About";
const description = "About - Programs Fall Apart";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main id="main-content">
    <SiteHeader />
    <section>
      <div>
        <p>Hey there, I’m Amira (ah-mee-rah).</p>
        <p>
          I started in mathematics, the kind where everything is provable and
          nothing decays. Then I stumbled into software engineering, where
          everything decays and very little is provable. I stayed anyway.
        </p>

        <p>
          I don’t claim mastery over any of this. I’m a curious programmer with
          a skeptical mind and a habit of pulling on threads until the whole
          thing unravels. Most of what you’ll find here was written on those
          nights, you know the ones, when a quick fix spirals into three hours
          of asking why, and by the time you look up, the coffee beside you has
          gone cold and the room is different.
        </p>

        <p>
          This isn’t a place for answers. It’s where I write things down before
          I forget the shape of them. I’ll get things wrong. That’s part of it.
        </p>

        <p>
          If something here made you pause, even for a second, I’m a comment, an <a
            href="mailto:amira@programsfallapart.com">email</a
          >, or a <a
            href="https://twitter.com/pfa_amira"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >twitter <span class="sr-only">(opens in new tab)</span></a
          ><sup class="footnote">*</sup> away. I’d like to know your name too.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="about-footnote">
        * Yes, I know it's called X now. No, I will not be calling it that.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-footnote {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond";
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
</style>
